Other items in
winsafe::co

Struct winsafe::co::HRESULT[−][src]

#[repr(transparent)]
pub struct HRESULT(_);
This is supported on crate feature ole only.
Expand description

A native COM error code (u32).

Implements the standard Error trait.

Implements the Debug and Display traits to show the error code along with the error description, taken from FormattedError trait. For example, the code below:

use winsafe::prelude::*;
use winsafe::co::HRESULT;

println!("{}", HRESULT::E_INVALIDARG);

Will print:

[0x80070057 2147942487] The parameter is incorrect.
